<title>恐怖寒潮袭击美东影响8000万人，全纽约公交停运，已致8人死亡</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/qKubkqfmOk</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/qKubkqfmOk</guid>
<description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.850091407678245&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iazVyianA9Miaibia5CkT1AwQVjcy3CZIS8Cyc0M9icvgSSiaPJWLzLnywq4quQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;547&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;近日，一场突如其来的寒潮袭击了美国东北部地区，导致了6英寸厚的降雪。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;这场寒潮也导致整个纽约市的公交系统停运，数十万人通勤困难。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;与此同时也造成了8人死亡。&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.9042663891779397&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iazNkTlWuznL19YemFXzBumayo7jZTCmRAqr8z8FlDKGEbyhzHO8Bmxkg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;961&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.3336798336798337&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iaz9UTLnZUnicDJEgVPd0iaGyhR6ZmvibtH915Dg8zQicKU9oGtewfAxSySWg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;962&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;因为公交系统整体停运，导致上万人拥堵在纽约诸如port authority这样的公交总枢纽。&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6642411642411642&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iazIXTriaZmJo40mkk3bCM6k7J41wnL3QZXdfQaMuhglJsAmMUiatBvHeYg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;962&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;几乎全部进出纽约的长途巴士也被迫停运了。&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6860706860706861&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iazKDSmuX4BYvjmPh7WgnRScPBSdz6JhjicYdEgkHqUTWduVYtjyVkNumg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;962&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.4282744282744282&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iazyhbUkiaudGzsAPueIFrv8ZxhFCQDYnetTMwrA0fC4yBVesjmHL8I36g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;962&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;一名市民走过世界贸易中心。&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6964656964656964&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iazjVeDSKxI29ibcCPRwS9uw5NuB02ZrAobFibvebLWtJfjibMBBIiapb49vQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;962&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;纽约地区最大的雪有6英寸厚。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7006237006237006&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iazhzzdFO4HpU8yaLpWuKzFHgPNCDceuQMpGOEHH3iaF6TiawmhN51ATSzQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;962&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7328482328482329&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iazic0FicFcbBsTD5bySzicMUdu3F9VaTUGkIfLjvh7XZEKuSsl7cc4zRdjw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;962&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6673596673596673&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iaz4deNsdWNsaOjpTeWgJlhQBMxo8OtQYZrribuEjp9viarGhlbhiaw9eJAA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;962&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6455301455301455&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iazgicxYYia6OKUkNib9CZPxSC2WoO8qgZV8F5ic9Micm3KWfSialYLCLIOkAiaQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;962&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;大雪也导致了多辆公交车事故，整个公交系统被迫停运。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6663201663201663&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iaz6FyYYmMK25hy1ibfIfGUmic8MTMWeyHKGJ4O3CbMibVEaz4RABa1bRjTg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;962&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;从纽约波士顿到华盛顿DC都普降大雪。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;据专家推测，寒潮和降雪将覆盖从圣路易斯到纽约华盛顿这一大片地区。&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;有464个航班被取消，1946个航班遭延误。&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6663201663201663&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xAict4B2y2K6N0jibEXJj03iazuQLZEQn7ciaoXY9A0ibPTicJwtib12Uw4hcqGLCHXIWyZVhra8LtPMJEjw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;962&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
